Class OsgiAbstractJobProducer

java.lang.Object
org.opencastproject.job.api.AbstractJobProducer
org.opencastproject.job.api.OsgiAbstractJobProducer
All Implemented Interfaces:
JobProducer
Direct Known Subclasses:
NopServiceImpl
public abstract class OsgiAbstractJobProducer extends AbstractJobProducer
Refined implementation of AbstractJobProducer suitable for use in an OSGi environment. OSGi dependency injection methods are provided to reduce the amount of boilerplate code needed per service implementation.
